Package: bayesiangpu
Title: GPU-Accelerated Bayesian Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("BayesianGPU", "Authors", email = "team@bayesiangpu.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: GPU-accelerated Bayesian inference using the No-U-Turn Sampler (NUTS).
    Provides a fluent API for building Bayesian models and running MCMC sampling
    with automatic convergence diagnostics (R-hat, ESS). Built on top of a Rust
    core library for performance.
